p.k: Granville plans a double date with Madge and Mavis but needs to smarten up Gastric. There's more romance in the air as Mrs. Featherstone has her heart set on a new husband and Nurse Gladys is wooed by a former patient. (2015). Cast: David Jason, Lynda Baron, James Baxter, Stephanie Cole, Maggie Ollerenshaw, Brigit Forsyth, Johnny Vegas, Kulvinder Ghir, Nina Wadia, Tim Healy. Director: Dewi Humphreys.
